query:
SELECT tp.id, u.name, u.email, tp.approvalStatus 
FROM tutor_profiles tp 
JOIN users u ON tp.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.email IN ('maya.b@edkonnect.com', 'shriti.s@edkonnect.com');
